tructions.</span> </li> <li style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; text-transform: none;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">We may request proof of payment (e.g., MT103, FPT, or bank transfer confirmation).</span> </li> <li style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; text-transform: none;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Only authorized individuals, as per the OTC Trading Counterparty Agreement, may issue instructions.</span> </li> </ul> <div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;margin-bottom:10px;"> <br><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Required Details:</span> </div> <ol style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"> <li style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; text-transform: none;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Fiat Funding Bank Account (Currency, Country)</span> </li> <li style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; text-transform: none;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Receiving Wallet Address &amp; Token Ticker Symbol (e.g., BTC, ETH, USDT)</span> </li> </ol> </div> </div> </td> </tr> </table> <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation"> <tr> <td valign="top" style="padding: 20px 0px 20px 0px;"> <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation"> <tr> <td valign="top" style="line-height: 1px; font-size: 1px; border-bottom: 1