ils:</span> </div> <ol style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 400;"> <li style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; text-transform: none;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Transferring Wallet Address &amp; Token Ticker Symbol</span> </li> <li style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px; text-transform: none;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Beneficiary Bank Details (Currency, IBAN/SWIFT, Account Holder Name)</span> </li> </ol> </div> </div> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> <!-- END MODULE: Text --> </td> </tr> <tr> <td valign="top"> <!-- BEGIN MODULE: Image --> <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" role="presentation"> <tr> <td style="padding: 10px 0px 0px 0px;" width="100%" role="presentation"> <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" role="presentation"> <tr> <td valign="top" class="pc-w520-padding-5-0-15-0 pc-w620-padding-5-0-15-0" style="height: unset; background-color: transparent;" bgcolor="transparent"> <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation"> <tr> <td valign="top"> <img src="https://github.com/georgepanayides/lydiamemails/blob/main/Forex.png?raw=true" width="600" height="auto" alt="" style="display: block; outline: 0; line-height: 100%; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; width: 100%; height: auto; border: 0;" /> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> <!-- END MODULE: Image --> </td> </tr> <tr> <td valign="top"> <!-- BEGIN MODULE: Text --> <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" role="presentation"> <tr> <td style="padding: 10px 0px 0px 0px;" width="100%" role=