 21px;">For BTC, ETH, USDT, or other token deposits, please reach out to your Lydiam Group contact or email us directly at dealing@lydiamgroup.com to receive your client-segregated wallet address.</span> </div> <div> <br> </div> <div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Trading Communication Channels:</span> </div> <div> <br> </div> <div style="color:#333333;font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:400;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Execution, balance updates, and settlement requests will be securely conducted via Telegram or Email. Ensure that any communication originates from pre-authorized accounts.</span> </div> <div> <br> </div> <div style="font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Settlements &amp; Authorizations:</span> </div> <div> <br> </div> <div style="color:#333333;font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:400;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Updates to wallet addresses or bank details must be initiated by approved individuals only. No instructions will be actioned without verification.</span> </div> <div> <br> </div> <div style="color:#333333;font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:400;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 21px;">Should you require further clarification or wish to discuss your onboarding in greater detail, our team is readily available. We thank you for choosing Lydiam Group and look forward to a long-standing and successful relationship.</span> </div> <div> <br> </div> <div style="color:#333333;font-family:'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight:400;"><span style="font-family: 'Arial', Helvetica, sans-serif; 